<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Mort </PERSON> <PERSON> Rosenblum </PERSON>, who is based in <LOCATION> Paris </LOCATION>, covered <LOCATION> Southeast </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Asia </LOCATION> in the 1970s and has reported subsequently on Cambodian problems.
