conomic growth,'' she said. The <ORGANIZATION> U.S. </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Commerce </ORGANIZATION> is to release the nation's July jobless rate Friday in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
