<ORGANIZATION> University </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Chicago </ORGANIZATION> in 1949. He is survived by his wife, <PERSON> Stephanie </PERSON> <PERSON> Gervis </PERSON> <PERSON> Harrington </PERSON>, and two sons. Private cremation services were held Tuesday. A memorial is planned for September at <ORGANIZATION> Queens </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> College </ORGANIZATION>.
