<TEXT>
 <PERSON> John </PERSON> <PERSON> Daniszewski </PERSON>, the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION> correspondent in <LOCATION> Warsaw </LOCATION>, has covered <LOCATION> Poland </LOCATION> since 1987.
