champions freedom of expression for writers and had stayed out of the <LOCATION> Soviet </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Union </LOCATION> because of its persecution of writers and other intellectuals. The change of heart came after <PERSON> Mikhail </PERSON> <PERSON> S. </PERSON> <PERSON> Gorbachev </PERSON> introduced more liberal policies.
