<FIRST>a a PM-ReligionRoundup Adv04   08-02 0552</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Religion Roundup, Adv 04,0572</SECOND>
<HEAD>$adv04</HEAD>
<HEAD>For release Fri PM Aug. 4, or thereafter</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WHEATON, Ill. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
